snippet.title: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 - The Vet & The n00b Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 live action trailer featuring Sam Worthington, Jonah Hill and Dwight Howard. Whether you're a veteran of Call of Duty or a n00b just starting out, there is a soldier in all of us.

ESRB Rating: MATURE 17+ (Blood and Gore, Drug Reference, Intense Violence, and Strong Language)
